#

Warm Vegetable Salad

25 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyWarmVegetables

Description

A colorful mix of roasted vegetables served warm, drizzled with a tangy balsamic dressing.

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 1 medium
  • bell pepper: 1
  • carrot: 1 large
  • red onion: 1 small
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh basil: a handful (optional)
